These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, 7up, tea
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tea-polo, lacrosse, ice-hockey, climbing
1. the person who's sport is tea-polo is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
2. the person drinking fanta is not the person who's sport is tea-polo##6
3. the person who's sport is tea-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is tea-polo##1
6. the person who's sport is tea-polo is not the person drinking 7up##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | fanta   | tea    | almond-milk    | 7up |
| Sport      | climbing | tea-polo | ice-hockey | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, water, lemonade, 7up
There 4 different types of food: lemon, asparagus, pomegranate, papaya
1. the person eating lemon is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5
3. the person eating papaya is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
4. the person drinking water is not the person eating asparagus##6
5. the person eating papaya is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
7. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
8. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | water  | lemonade    | tea | 7up    |
| Food       | papaya | asparagus | pomegranate  | lemon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea, mirinda, 7up
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, architect, entrepreneur, accountant
1. the person drinking 7up is not the fisherman##6
2. the architect is not the person drinking mirinda##6
3. the entrepreneur is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
4. the architect is the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the left of the architect##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is in an odd position##4
7. the fisherman is on the far left or far right##3
8. the entrepreneur is somewhere to the left of the accountant##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | 7up       | tea  | soy-milk  | mirinda |
| Job        | entrepreneur | accountant | architect | fisherman  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, rabbit, pony, rat
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, scooter, jet-ski, tram
1. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5
3. the person driving the tram is not the owner of the rabbit##6
4. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the right of the person driving the helicopter##5
5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
6. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | rabbit | pony | rat     | bird |
| Transport   | scooter     | jet-ski    | helicopter | tram    |

