.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, almond-milk, juice, sprite
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, motorbike, quad-bike, trike
1. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
3. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5
4. the person drinking almond-milk is not the person driving the trike##6
5. the person driving the tram is not the person drinking water##6
6. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
7. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | water        | sprite | juice | almond-milk |
| Transport   | trike | tram | motorbike     | quad-bike   |

