.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, comedy, documentary, romance
There are 4 different nationalities: french, argentine, chinese, nigerian
1. the french is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
2. the person watching romance movies is not the argentine##6
3. the french is on the far right##1
4. the argentine is somewhere to the right of the nigerian##5
5. the person watching documentary movies is the person watching documentary movies##1
6. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the left of the french##5
7. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching satire movies##5
8. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5
9. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | documentary    | satire  | romance   |
| Nationality   | chinese  | nigerian | argentine | french |

