.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, scientific, comedy, adventure
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, dubstep, disco, soul
1. the fan disco is on the left or right of the fan ambient##3
2. the fan disco is not the person watching scientific movies##6
3. the person watching western movies is the fan dubstep##1
4. the fan ambient is on the left or right of the fan soul##3
5. the fan disco is on the far left##1
6. the person watching scientific movies is the fan ambient##1
7. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the left of the fan ambient##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | scientific     | comedy | western |
| Music-Genre   | disco | ambient | soul      | dubstep         |

