.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea, lemonade, juice
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, dressmaker, accountant, bartender
1. the lawyer is on the left of the dressmaker##1
2. the bartender is somewhere to the left of the accountant##5
3. the bartender is on the right of the dressmaker##1
4. the dressmaker is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3
6. the lawyer is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
7. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
8. the person drinking iced-tea is not the bartender##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | iced-tea  | hot-chocolate        | lemonade      | juice          |
| Job        | lawyer | dressmaker | bartender | accountant |

