.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, paramedic, chef, social-worker
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, trike, train, taxi
1. the freelancer is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the trike is not the social-worker##6
3. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the chef##5
4. the person driving the taxi is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the train##1
6. the person driving the taxi is the chef##1
7. the freelancer is not the person driving the taxi##6
8. the paramedic is somewhere to the right of the social-worker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | freelancer  | chef | social-worker    | paramedic |
| Transport   | trike | taxi | train | car  |

