.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, lizard, snake, cat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, volleyball, handball, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is cycling is not the owner of the mouse##6
2. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
5. the owner of the snake is not the person who's sport is snowboarding##6
6. the person who's sport is volleyball is not the owner of the lizard##6
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the snake is the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | snake | mouse        | cat  | lizard     |
| Sport   | cycling     | snowboarding | volleyball | handball |

