.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, video-games, collecting, board-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, house, d&b, funk
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
2. the fan house is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5
3. the fan d&b is not the person who's hobby is collecting##6
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the fan funk and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
6. the fan house is between the fan r&b and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | collecting | video-games    | magic-tricks | board-games |
| Music-Genre   | r&b         | house | funk   | d&b     |

