.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-12::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, raspberry, tomato, orange
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, subway, helicopter, skateboard
1. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the right of the person driving the helicopter##5
2. the person eating orange is not the person driving the quad-bike##6
3. the person driving the subway is the person eating orange##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
5. the person driving the helicopter is not the person eating orange##6
6. the person eating raspberry is not the person driving the quad-bike##6
7. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the left of the person eating raspberry##5
8. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person eating tomato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | kiwi  | tomato | raspberry | orange |
| Transport   | helicopter | quad-bike     | skateboard     | subway    |

