.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-13::.
There 4 different types of food: corn, apple, pepper, pineapple
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, drama, animation, martial-arts
1. the person eating corn is somewhere to the right of the person eating apple##5
2. the person eating apple is not the person watching drama movies##6
3. the person eating corn is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the person eating pepper is somewhere to the right of the person watching drama movies##5
5. the person eating corn is between the person eating apple and the person watching zombie movies##2
6. the person eating apple is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | pineapple | apple      | corn | pepper   |
| Movie-Genre   | drama     | animation | martial-arts   | zombie |

