3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the scooter is not the person who's sport is climbing##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | cricket | rowing | climbing | tennis |
| Transport   | tram   | van       | motorbike    | scooter     |

