6. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
8. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |       3       |       4       |
