.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, cooking, rock-climbing, baking
4 different pets are kept: ferret, bird, rat, goldfish
1. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5
2. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the right of the owner of the bird##5
3. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is not the person who's hobby is puzzles##6
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
6. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
8. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the bird##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | cooking | rock-climbing | puzzles | baking |
| Pet     | rat  | bird      | ferret  | goldfish       |

