4. the person driving the boat is not the person drinking juice##6
5. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person driving the car##5
6. the person driving the car is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | juice | lemonade | 7up      | coffee   |
| Transport   | ship  | car   | bike | boat |

 